snippet.title: DeTechtive 2112 Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
SUPORT US!: https://patreon.com/m11studio

What is DeTechtive?
"DeTechtive 2112" is an action and adventure game set in a futuristic cyber universe about a private detective. The game features a shooter genre, offering players an isometric perspective camera experience.
